This is giving me the impression that Sleeper is involved, and part of the sequince of events that leads to the war will be the awakening of Sleeper.<br>
<br>
Toward the end of the Firona/Tunare/Cazic event, Firona is told she must visit with the Ring of Scale on the next step of her journey.  Perhaps Firona Vie is supposed to be the one that wakes the sleeper first, and this is one of the reasons VI was all twisted out of shape about the incident ... because it was going to give away part of the storyline.<br>
