________________________________________<br>
<br>
Last Night, in the mountains of Steamfont I was told of a strange collection of foreigners who had gathered about the Wind Mill for some sort of Congress.<br>
<br>
Amongst the strangers was Zavo'Zatanov (Scholar of the Ring of Scale apparently), Ashteth T'Dral (High Priest of Innoruk), Irin'Ka Set (Informant to Trakanon and betrayer of the Ring of Scale) and Mayong Mistmoore as the topper. They gathered and spoke of the state of Norrath and the war against exstinction it must fight. Lanys has fallen from Innoruk's grace and seeks to steal his power with the staff Malevolence. Trakanon is to aid her. It was around this point Irin'Ka Set revealed his true self to Zavo, at which point they both turned to dragons and battled over the peaks at Steamfont. Zavo'Zatanov won over the betrayer.<br>
<br>
After this was secure, the charecters present determined that with the gem to complete molevloence in Mayong's posession, Norrath had nothing to fear...but be on your guard they warned...and do not fall to the tricks of Lanys<br>
