Dark Tidings on Quellious! -GM Event<br>
Evan Cooney [6/26/2001-11:35:53 AM]  Comments[1]<br>
<br>
Friends, I come to you with dire news. Al`Kabor, the mighty wizard who has for so long fought alongside Tunare's Chosen, Firiona Vie, and her allies has turned against the light. In his obsessive quest for magical knowledge, Al`Kabor has forsaken sense and consorts now with the Teir`Dal in hopes of quick and easy gain. He spouts rhetoric saying to 'wait for the future to unfold' to try and make us complacent and ignore his dealings in the present... with his current behavior there will be no future!<br>
<br>
Lanys T`Vyl's faction grows stronger, and Tunare finds herself and her creations under attack from dark forces, as has oh so recently occured in the Faydark, but still this wizard stands by and speaks only of his own benefit. This became obvious today in the Dreadlands where Al`Kabor declared his desire only for personal magical gain, and took as his agent a Teir`Dal sorcerer. Friends, this can not and must not be allowed to happen! Band together, aid the chosen of Tunare, and fight back against the darkness whereever it may occur! I shall be with you at the front, fighting the good fight against the forces of evil, and if neccessary, dying with the enemy's heart in my hands!<br>
<br>
